  "tx.faq.eyebrow": "Frequently asked",
  "tx.faq.h": "What you need to <span class=\"hi\">know about Trendex</span>",
  "tx.faq.q1.a": "Most ad networks take a large share of budgets for themselves. In Trendex, ad budgets flow directly to active users and the partner network — no classic middlemen, no hidden markups.",
  "tx.faq.q1.q": "How is Trendex different from regular ad networks?",
  "tx.faq.q2.a": "No. Basic registration is free, and payouts are earned for views and task completion. Paid plans add capabilities — optional, not required.",
  "tx.faq.q2.q": "Do I need to invest to start earning?",
  "tx.faq.q3.a": "Earnings land in your internal balance in real time. Withdrawals go through the supported payment methods. Every operation is visible in your dashboard.",
  "tx.faq.q3.q": "How do payouts work?",
  "tx.faq.q4.a": "Early participants receive a doubled ad budget on business-tier activation and lock in their network position. Pre-launch terms apply only until the official launch date.",
  "tx.faq.q4.q": "What do I get for joining before launch?",
  "tx.faq.q5.a": "Your dashboard includes: a builder for landings, funnels and bots, AI assistants, the Premium link shortener, Bio pages, a video-banner generator and regular updates. All without external subscriptions.",
  "tx.faq.q5.q": "What tools are available inside the platform?",
  "tx.faq.q6.a": "The exact date is published via the platform's official channels. Register now to get launch notifications and use the early access terms.",
  "tx.faq.q6.q": "When is launch?",
